item.title: CVE-2024-6020|2024-09-04T14:23:36.656Z -- unknown -- sign-up%20sheets
item.description: The Sign-up Sheets WordPress plugin before 2.2.13 does not escape some generated URLs, as well as the $_SERVER['REQUEST_URI'] parameter before outputting them back in attributes, which could lead to Reflected Cross-Site Scripting.
